 custom-designed furniture blending into a cohesive palette. These elements were carefully selected to foster a soothing environment, while durable and functional materials like terrazzo flooring add a layer of playful practicality to high-traffic areas like the kitchen and entrance.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=556542\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-556542\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/09/Playpod-Sanctuary-Hong-Kong-Bean-Buro-11-810x540.jpg\" alt=\"A modern home office with a wooden chair, desk, pegboard wall organizer, arched shelf, and large floor cushion. Floor-to-ceiling windows provide ample natural light.\" width=\"810\" height=\"540\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/09/Playpod-Sanctuary-Hong-Kong-Bean-Buro-11-810x540.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/09/Playpod-Sanctuary-Hong-Kong-Bean-Buro-11-800x533.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/09/Playpod-Sanctuary-Hong-Kong-Bean-Buro-11-768x512.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/09/Playpod-Sanctuary-Hong-Kong-Bean-Buro-11.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=556543\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-556543\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/09/Playpod-Sanctuary-Hong-Kong-Bean-Buro-12-810x1013.jpg\" alt=\"A modern interior featuring curved architectural elements, a staircase with wooden steps on the left, geometric floor patterns, and built-in seating with pastel-colored cushions.\" width=\"810\" height=\"1013\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/09/Playpod-Sanctuary-Hong-Kong-Bean-Buro-12-810x1013.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/09/Playpod-Sanctuary-Hong-Kong-Bean-Buro-12-800x1000.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com