ght green railing and slatted design. Wooden flooring and wall, with an arched window in the background overlooking a garden.\" width=\"810\" height=\"1215\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/09/Playpod-Sanctuary-Hong-Kong-Bean-Buro-14-810x1215.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/09/Playpod-Sanctuary-Hong-Kong-Bean-Buro-14-800x1200.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/09/Playpod-Sanctuary-Hong-Kong-Bean-Buro-14-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/09/Playpod-Sanctuary-Hong-Kong-Bean-Buro-14-1024x1536.jpg 1024w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/09/Playpod-Sanctuary-Hong-Kong-Bean-Buro-14.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=556546\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-556546\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/09/Playpod-Sanctuary-Hong-Kong-Bean-Buro-15-810x546.jpg\" alt=\"A modern bedroom with a low-profile bed, neutral bedding, a floor lamp, and sheer curtains covering large windows. A framed picture is resting against the wall on the wooden floor.\" width=\"810\" height=\"546\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/09/Playpod-Sanctuary-Hong-Kong-Bean-Buro-15-810x546.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/09/Playpod-Sanctuary-Hong-Kong-Bean-Buro-15-800x539.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/09/Playpod-Sanctuary-Hong-Kong-Bean-Buro-15-768x518.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/09/Playpod-Sanctuary-Hong-Kong-Bean-Buro-15.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=556547\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-556547\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/09/Playpod-Sanctuary-Hong-Kong-Bean-Buro-16-810x1013.jpg